---
// Urgency.astro - countdown / fear section before checkout
---

<section class="urgency-section" aria-labelledby="urgency-heading">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <div class="urgency-card">
      <div class="fire-emoji" aria-hidden="true">🔥🔥🔥</div>
      <h2 id="urgency-heading">
        Setiap Hari Tanpa Software Ini,<br/>
        <span class="text-red">Kamu Kehilangan Rp 300.000+ Komisi Potensial.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="urgency-desc">
        Bayangkan punya 20 akun TikTok, masing-masing upload 5 video per hari. Itu <strong>100 video per hari</strong> yang berpotensi menghasilkan komisi.
        Sekarang, berapa video yang sanggup kamu upload secara manual? 10? 20?
        <strong>Kompetitor kamu sudah di 100.</strong>
      </p>
      <div class="fear-stats" aria-label="Perbandingan kemampuan upload per hari">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-num stat-bad" aria-label="Upload manual per hari">10–20</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Upload/hari (manual)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-vs" aria-hidden="true">VS</div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-num stat-good" aria-label="Upload dengan software per hari">100+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Upload/hari (dengan software)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="warning-box" role="alert" aria-live="polite">
        <strong>⚠️ Peringatan:</strong> Harga promo <strong>Rp 374.250 dengan kode DISKON25%</strong> hanya berlaku untuk <strong>waktu terbatas.</strong> Setelah kuota habis, harga kembali ke Rp 499.000.
      </div>
      <a href="https://prodig.deskomvis.com/checkout-tiktok-autopost" class="urgency-btn" aria-label="Amankan harga promo terbatas sekarang">
        <span aria-hidden="true">🛒</span> Amankan Aksesmu Sebelum Terlambat
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .urgency-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fef2f2 0%, #fff7f7 100%);
  }

  .urgency-card {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 50px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.12);
    border: 2px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.12);
  }

  .fire-emoji {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }

  .text-red {
    color: #dc2626;
  }

  .urgency-desc {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .fear-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .stat-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 24px 40px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: #f8fafc;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    min-width: 160px;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .stat-bad { color: #dc2626; }
  .stat-good { color: #16a34a; }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .stat-vs {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #9ca3af;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .warning-box {
    background: #fef3c7;
    border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    color: #78350f;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    animation: shake 6s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes shake {
    0%, 90%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
    92% { transform: translateX(-4px); }
    94% { transform: translateX(4px); }
    96% { transform: translateX(-4px); }
    98% { transform: translateX(4px); }
  }

  .urgency-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    padding: 18px 40px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.45);
    transition: all 0.3s;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--font-family);
  }

  .urgency-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 30px -5px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.55);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .urgency-card { padding: 40px 20px; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.7rem; }
    .fear-stats { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; align-items: stretch; }
    .stat-item { padding: 20px; }
  }
</style>
